------------------------------------------------------------------------
Vendored third-party / first-party sources
------------------------------------------------------------------------

For convenience and to make the open-source build fully self-contained,
this repository vendors source from the following first-party GAL
packages under `src/vendored-gal/` (Apache-2.0, same as this repo):

  - @gal/types         -> src/vendored-gal/types
  - @gal/core          -> src/vendored-gal/core
  - @gal/swarm         -> src/vendored-gal/swarm
  - @gal/telemetry     -> src/vendored-gal/telemetry (+ src/lib/gal-telemetry-browser.ts)
  - @gal/enforce-rules -> src/vendored-gal/enforce-rules

The Enterprise repository/client layer (@gal/api client) is vendored
under `src/ee/vendored-gal-api/` and is covered by the GAL Enterprise
License (see src/ee/LICENSE), consistent with the rest of `src/ee/`.
